Master’s Degree in Finance, Economics, Accounting or related field required. CA certificate/RA
certificate is preferred;
10+ years’ experience working in Technical Accounting or related field required;
Experience with running an accounting department, VAT declarations, treasury management;
Prior experience in a commodity or energy trading firm preferred;
Experience with accounting and reporting software, ERP systems and databases;
Knowledge of Hyperion is a pre;
